ructure-based rating of roost potential supplemented by species-specific microclimatic requirements constitutes a promising predictor of roost usage. Moreover, adequate buildings support the complete life cycle of R. hipposideros in the absence of suitable caves. Buildings thus deserve increased protection measures in fragmented Mediterranean landscapes to ensure sustainable bat conservation.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Winter, Rebecca", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mantilla-Contreras, Jasmin", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Schmidt, Sabine", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/e3fa05281d9f482f5e459c15079427db", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/86cf6a462bd48757abb339927329292f383450bd49e14c4bc3e0451185d5403a", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/CHTH3LZG", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/CHTH3LZG", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/3938642318353154b1e51d96ac6dbd40!/b56894-59357", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "3", "pages": "38", "title": "European Journal of Wildlife Research", "volume": "66"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/e3fa05281d9f482f5e459c15079427db"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid: